title: NEWLYWED GAME! Bones vs. Pardi + Jon Pardi Performs HITS In Studio! + Best and Worst Christmas Songs
itunes:title: NEWLYWED GAME! Bones vs. Pardi + Jon Pardi Performs HITS In Studio! + Best and Worst Christmas Songs
description:
Jon Pardi stops by the studio with his bride to be, Summer to challenge Bobby and Caitlin in the Newlywed Game! Jon also performs a few of his hits for us! Plus, we get into the Christmas spirit by revealing our favorite and least favorite Christmas songs!
